These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: grapes, asparagus
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, woodworking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts
1. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
2. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | water      |
| Food          | asparagus | grapes    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | martial-arts      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, designer
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, roller
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5
3. the designer is not to the right of the analyst##8
4. the person driving the van is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | juice        | coffee    |
| Hobby       | writing         | sudoku |
| Job         | designer | analyst   |
| Transport   | van               | roller  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, animation
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, salsa
There are 2 different nationalities: british, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: frog, pony
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the nigerian is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
3. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | animation |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | salsa    |
| Nationality   | british | nigerian |
| Pet           | frog        | pony   |

