.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, bartender
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, argentine
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski
1. the indian is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | woodworking  |
| Job           | bartender  | dancer |
| Nationality   | argentine | indian   |
| Transport     | jet-ski   | scooter |

